T02TD1779E:273a-1: shr'i ma h'a k'a la s+yashta mantra sto tra n'a ma /
T02TD1779E:273a-3: dpal nag po chen po la bstod pa rkang pa brgyad pa zhes bya ba /
T02TD1779E:273a-4: dpal nag po chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1779E:273a-5: aom grub par gyur cig / h'um h'um phat ces drag po'i sgra yis srid pa gsum gyi khong ni ma lus 'gengs nus pa'i //
T02TD1779E:273b-0: ha ha ta ta zhes bzhad sgra yis gang zhig dus kun du ni shin tu 'jigs mdzad @273b cing ;
T02TD1779E:273b-1: / kam kam kam zhes thod pa'i phreng bas dbu la spras shing nag po'i mthu dang mtshungs pa'i sku //
T02TD1779E:273b-2: bhrum bhrum bhrum zhes khros pa'i mchog gi khro gnyer 'jigs mdzad 'jigs pa'i khva gdangs sha za zhing //
T02TD1779E:273b-3: dbu skra dang ni smar ches ser nye bar spyod pa'i zhing skyod khyod kyis srung bar mdzod //
T02TD1779E:273b-4: ram ram ram zhes spyan mar 'khrug cing bsgyur mdzad krum krum krum zhes rab sgrogs spyan gyis gzigs //
T02TD1779E:273b-5: smin ma ser zhing mche gtsigs ro yi gdan la dgyes pa'i zhing skyong khyod kyis zhing skyong mdzod //
T02TD1779E:273b-6: ha ha h'um dang k'i li k'i li zhes sgrogs phyag g-yon kha tv'am gar bcas thod pa bsnams //
T02TD1779E:273b-7: ru ru ru zhes khrag rgyun 'bab pa phyag gis bsnams shing gsol ba 'thungs pa la dgyes shing //
T02TD1779E:273b-8: kham kham kham zhes gtum pa'i phyag g-yas gri gug ral gri bgegs rnams la ni rol mdzad pa'i //
T02TD1779E:273b-9: tam tam tam zhes da ma ru can 'di yis 'dul tshad 'khor bcas zhing skyong khyod kyis srungs //
T02TD1779E:273b-10: rab tu rngam zhing mgo bo rnams kyi phreng bas gshin rje dang mtshungs 'jigs pa'i sku brgyan cing //
T02TD1779E:273b-11: ksham ksham ksham zhes bzod pa'i thugs can ca co sgrogs par byed pa'i gdug pa rnams bzung ste //
T02TD1779E:273b-12: gcig pus sna tshogs mnan cing mnan nas ha ka ha ka brjod mdzad char sprin sngon po'i mdog / sku la mi yi sha dang rgyu mas brel ba'i rgyan gyis kun nas brgyan cing zhal du gsol //
T02TD1779E:273b-13: drag shul phyag gis 'dod pa'i gzugs dang mi sdug gzugs can gyi ni 'byung bo ro langs tshogs //
T02TD1779E:273b-14: ma lus bzung nas myur du bsad pa rnams kyi mgo bo'i khrag rgyun 'bab pa rab tu gsol //
T02TD1779E:273b-15: hrim kshim shr'im gi sngags kyi gsungs can pa tsa pa tsa'i sngags kyis bgegs rnams rab tu sreg / rol pas rol pa sel zhing mi yis gang ba'i mtsho la zhing skyong khyod kyis srung bar mdzad //
T02TD1779E:273b-16: phem phem phat ces sgrogs pa so sor bskyod pa'i me dpung chen po'i dbus su bzhugs nas su //
T02TD1779E:273b-17: rigs kyi lus can srung bar mdzod cig sgrub bo rnams kyi zhing rnams nges par skyong mdzod cig / phyugs rnams kyis ni nyin ra bzhin du bgegs dang sdig 'joms dri med brnyes pa chu nyi bzhin //
T02TD1779E:274a-0: tsam tsam tsam zhes gtum po'i shugs kyis rab g-yos rmad byung 'od kyis 'jig rten snang mdzad @274a * //
T02TD1779E:274a-2: / krim krim krim zhes gshegs pas dgra bo nyon mongs pa rnams nges par nyon mongs 'joms mdzad cing //
T02TD1779E:274a-3: sam sam sam zhes tshogs pa'i bdag nyid dag thos cing 'dzin zhing skyong gang yin khyod kyis skyongs //
T02TD1779E:274a-4: bam bam bam zhes gshin rje ltar 'gro dri ma med pa'i sna tshogs chu bzhin gzigs mdzad cing //
T02TD1779E:274a-5: yam yam yam zhes rlung gi shugs kyis myur du rgyu zhing nyon mongs 'jig rten gnod byed mkhyen //
T02TD1779E:274a-6: klam klim klum zhes gdug pa'i gzugs kyis srid gsum nyin mtshan dus kun nyon mongs gyur pa gang //
T02TD1779E:274a-7: pam pam pam zhes thugs rje'i zhags pas byol song rnams 'dzin phyag gis gdul bya rnams skyong ba //
T02TD1779E:274a-8: sngags bdag sngags kyi lus can thugs kyi sngags pa rnams la 'bras bu blo gros mtshungs med ster //
T02TD1779E:274a-9: zhing rnams skyod bar mdzad pa khyod kyis 'gro ba'i lus rnams ma lus yun ring bskyang du gso //
T02TD1779E:274a-10: sgrub pa po yi slob dpon 'ga' zhig dam tshig gang zhig blo ldan gus pa yi //
T02TD1779E:274a-11: thung nyis su ni sngags rnams brgyad po klog byed de ni bsod nams ldan par gyur pa dang //
T02TD1779E:274a-12: tshe dang dpal dang grags dang mthu stobs 'byor ba 'dzin dang gzi brjid rgyas pa mtshungs pa med //
T02TD1779E:274a-13: sa steng dang ni mtho ris su'ang de yi bgegs kyi tshogs rnams rtag tu nyams par 'gyur //
T02TD1779E:274a-14: dpal nag po chen po la bstod ba rkang pa brgyad pa zhes bya ba /
T02TD1779E:274a-15: slob dpon chen po 'phags pa klu sgrub kyi zhal mnga' nas mdzad pa'o //
T02TD1779E:274a-16: rgya gar gyi mkhan po shri bee ro tsa na badzra dang /
T02TD1779E:274a-17: bod kyi lo ts'a ba bande ldi ri chos grags kyis bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o//
